t; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;Son beneficios\r\nDEL CONTRATADO, los siguientes:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo7&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;1)&lt;span style=&quot;font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;Percibir la contraprestación mensual acordada.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo7&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;2)&lt;span style=&quot;font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;Gozar de veinticuatro (24) horas continuas mínimas de descanso por\r\nsemana. Dicho descanso se tomará todos los días domingos de cada semana, salvo\r\npacto en contrario.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo7&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;3)&lt;span style=&quot;font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;Descansar quince (15) días calendario continuo por año cumplido.\r\nPara el ejercicio de este descanso; a falta de acuerdo, decidirá LA ENTIDAD.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo7&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;4)&lt;span style=&quot;font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;Gozar efectivamente de las prestaciones de salud de ESSALUD. En\r\nestos casos para el goce de las prestaciones de ESSALUD los beneficiarios\r\ndeberán cumplir con el período de carencia.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo7&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;5)&lt;span style=&quot;font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;Afiliación a un régimen de pensiones.&amp;nbsp; continuar en el Régimen que está afiliada.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo7&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;6)&lt;span style=&quot;font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;Los demás derechos establecidos en el Decreto Legislativos Nº 1057\r\ny su reglamento del decreto Supremo Nº075-2008-PCM.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;CLÁUSULA OCTAVA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;: &lt;b&gt;CONTRAPRESTACIÓN\r\nY FORMA DE PAGO&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;La contraprestación\r\nde los servicios se pacta en {{REMUNERACION}}&lt;b&gt;,\r\n&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;mensuales que serán abonados como\r\nmáximo, durante la última semana de cada mes.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;LA ENTIDAD hará efectiva la contraprestación\r\nconforme&amp;nbsp; a las disposiciones de\r\ntesorería que haya establecido el Ministerio de Economía y Finanzas y previa\r\npresentación del recibo por honorarios correspondientes por parte AL\r\nCONTRATADO.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;CLAUSULA NOVENA:&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;LUGAR DE\r\nPRESTACIÓN DEL SERVICIO.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;El &amp;nbsp;CONTRATADO&amp;nbsp;\r\nprestará los servicios &amp;nbsp;de &amp;nbsp;{{CARGO}}, &amp;nbsp;de la Municipalidad&amp;nbsp; Distrital de Lancones Provincia de Sullana\r\nDepartamento de Piura. La Entidad podrá disponer la prestación de servicios\r\nfuera del lugar designado de acuerdo a las necesidades de servicio definidas\r\npor LA ENTIDAD.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\ntext-indent:35.4pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;CLÁUSULA DECIMA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;: &lt;b&gt;GASTOS POR DESPLAZAMIENTO.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;En los casos en\r\nque sea necesario el traslado de la CONTRATADO en el ámbito nacional para el\r\ncumplimiento de las actividades materia del contrato, los gastos (pasajes,\r\nmovilidad, hospedaje, viáticos, y tarifa única por uso de aeropuerto) inherente\r\na estas actividades correrán por cuenta de LA ENTIDAD.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration:none&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration:none&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;CLÁUSULA DECIMO PRIMERA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;: &lt;b&gt;CAPACITACIÓN.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;EL CONTRATADO &amp;nbsp;podrá ser capacitado conforme a los Decretos\r\nLegislativos N°. 1023 y 1025 y de acuerdo a las necesidades institucionales.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;CLÁUSULA DECIMO SEGUNDA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;: &lt;b&gt;TÍTULOS\r\nDE PROPIEDAD Y CONFIDENCIALIDAD DE LA INFORMACIÓN.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;Las obras\r\ncreaciones intelectuales, científicas, entre otras, que se hayan realizado en\r\nel cumplimiento de las obligaciones del presente contrato con los recursos y\r\nmedios de la entidad, son de propiedad de la Entidad. En cualquier caso, los\r\ntítulos de propiedad, derechos de autor y todo otro tipo de derechos de\r\ncualquier naturaleza sobre cualquier material producido bajo las estipulaciones\r\nde este Contrato son cedidos a LA ENTIDAD en forma exclusiva.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;La información\r\nobtenida DEL CONTRATADO dentro del cumplimiento de sus obligaciones, así como\r\nsus informes y toda clase de documentos que produzca, relacionados con la\r\nejecución de sus labores será confidencial, no pudiendo ser divulgadas del &amp;nbsp;CONTRATADO.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;CLÁSULA DESIMO TERCERA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;: RESPONSABILIDAD\r\nDEL &amp;nbsp;CONTRATADO&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;La ENTIDAD para\r\nel mejor desarrollo de los fines materia del presente Contrato, podrá facilitar\r\ndel COTRATADO materiales y mobiliario, siendo responsable del &amp;nbsp;CONTRATADO del buen uso y conservación de los\r\nmismos, salvo el desgaste normal. En el caso de determinarse el incumplimiento\r\nde lo dispuesto en la presente cláusula, EL CONTRATADO deberá resarcir de manera\r\npecuniaria a LA ENTIDAD en proporción al daño ocasionado.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;CLÁUSULA DECIMO CUARTA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;: &lt;b&gt;CESIÓN&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;EL CONTRATADO no\r\npodrá transferir parcial ni totalmente las obligaciones contraídas en el\r\npresente contrato, siendo de su entera responsabilidad la ejecución y\r\ncumplimiento de las obligaciones establecidas en el mismo.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;CLÁUSULA DECIMO QUINTA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;: &lt;b&gt;CONFORMIDAD\r\nDEL SERVICIO.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;El servicio\r\nmateria del presente contrato estará bajo la supervisión &lt;b&gt;DEL JEFE DE LA UNIDAD DE RECURSOS HUMANOS DE LA MUNICIPALIDAD DISTRITAL\r\nDE LANCONES&lt;/b&gt;, quien permanentemente verificará el avance de la prestación del\r\nservicio, evaluando periódicamente los resultados obtenidos y estará facultada\r\na exigir al CONTRATADO la aplicación y cumplimiento de los términos del\r\npresente contrato, correspondiéndole, en su oportunidad, dar la conformidad de\r\ndicho servicio.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;CLÁUSULA DECIMO SEXTA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;: &lt;b&gt;EVALUACIÓN&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;EL CONTRATADO\r\npodrá ser evaluado por la Entidad, cuando lo estime necesario, conforme a lo\r\ndispuesto por los Decretos Legislativos Nº 1023 y 1025.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;CLÁUSULA DECIMO SETIMA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;: &lt;b&gt;SUPLENCIA\r\nY ENCARGO DE FUNCIONES&lt;/b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;De considerarlo\r\nconveniente&amp;nbsp; y, en la medida que la\r\nprestación del servicio asignado lo permite. LA ENTIDAD podrá designar al\r\nCONTRATADO como integrante titular o suplente de los Comités Especiales que se\r\nconformen de acuerdo a lo establecido en la D. L. Nº 1017- Ley Contrataciones\r\ndel Estado y su Reglamento, para llevar a cabo los procesos de selección que\r\nrequiere LA ENTIDAD.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNoSpacing&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Book Antiqua&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;serif&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot; lang=&quot;ES-PE&quot;&gt;Asimismo podrá\r\ndesignarlo a fin que represente a LA ENTIDAD ante Comisiones y Grupos de\r\nTrabajo que tuvieran relación co